column5: can anybody tell me what the duty on a case of beer & a bottle of booze is, thanks
Nothing if you buy from the locals. Local busineeses apppreciate the business. They might even let you in on a few hot spots.
Case of Beer 7$Whiskey bottle 15$Carton of Cigs 35$ Of course you get 1 bottle of whiskey OR 1 case of beer duty free per person. Also 1 carton of smokes duty free....Enjoy
YO MOOSE::That's $7 canadian per case. ummmm works out to be about 35 cents american
